comment._content: This picture may also be viewed here: www.aero-web.org/database/aircraft/getimage.htm?id=13908 'F4D over NAS North Island - San Diego, CA 1958' Distinctively decorated Douglas F4D-1 Skyray. Bu No 139097. VFAW-3. With tail code PA and ‘Modex’ nose code 12. ‘Last four’ of serial 9097 on base of rudder. Based at NAS North Island, San Diego, California. VFAW-3 was attached for a time to the North American Air Defense Command. (NORAD) Picture dated 1958. Anther ‘flickr’ pic with 139097 included, can be seen here: www.flickr.com/photos/my_public_domain_photos/4629797004/ Other lower resolution ‘flickr’ pictures of 139097 may also be seen here: www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559218451/ www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559218755/ www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559218563/ www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559849510/
